39
00:04:59,230 --> 00:05:03,570
I will only go where the major is.

40
00:05:04,780 --> 00:05:07,110
We're heading back to the office.

41
00:05:07,110 --> 00:05:10,120
You're one of our Auto Memoir Dolls, remember?

42
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:17,630
Fine, then. I'll stay here too.

43
00:05:18,130 --> 00:05:20,210
I'm not leaving until you come back with me.

44
00:05:21,630 --> 00:05:25,090
He entrusted me with you, after all.

45
00:05:27,260 --> 00:05:32,270
