46
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:38,270
Should anything happen to me, take care of Violet.

47
00:05:39,110 --> 00:05:45,570
Take her to the Evergarden
family in Leiden after the war is over.

48
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,820
Gilbert?

49
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:50,870
Please.

50
00:05:52,870 --> 00:05:57,750
He definitely didn't see you as a tool of warfare.

51
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:03,380
He was worried about your future as an ordinary girl.

52
00:06:19,690 --> 00:06:20,480
Hey, uh...

53
00:06:21,230 --> 00:06:22,860
