I wasn't sure if things would work out.

57
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:43,250
But you learned how to work as a Doll,

58
00:06:44,340 --> 00:06:46,590
and you put everything you had into it.

59
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:52,470
